<DESC>The purpose of this amendment is to revise the evaluation of offers and insert a revised statement of work.  Award will be made to the offeror whose proposal provides the best value to the Government, Technical, Price and Past Performance considered.  Each offeror shall submit a technical proposal that details their plan to mobilize, and how they intend to man the requirement.  Additionally, the contractor will provide a firm fixed price proposal for both CLINs 0001 and 1001.  Offerors shall provide past performance information for similar projects they have performed during the last three years.  In determining the best value to the Government technical is more important than price which is more more important than past performance.  A revised statement of work will be provided in amendment 06 due to size restrictions with fedbizopps.
